    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the meatballs are browned, add the <strong>sliced carrot </strong>to the pan and cook, covered, for 4-5 min or until starting to soften and the meatballs are cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Once soft, add your <strong>sugar snap peas </strong>and cook, uncovered, for 1 min further</p>",
